  m_text: 'When aproaching junctions, do this:

    1. Indicate where you''re going
    (use L2 / R2 for indicators)

    2. Slow down (for turning control)

    3.
    Check if there is oncoming traffic.

    4. Go when there is no oncoming traffic'
